Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/hatlabs/halos-imported-containers

Package: casaos-container-store
Architecture: all
Tag: role::container-store
Description: CasaOS container application store for Cockpit Container Apps
 This package provides the store definition and branding for the CasaOS
 container application store, designed to work with cockpit-container-apps.
 .
 When installed alongside cockpit-container-apps, it enables discovery and
 installation of 147+ auto-imported applications from the upstream CasaOS
 App Store.
 .
 Applications include media servers, home automation, productivity tools,
 networking utilities, storage solutions, and development platforms.
 .
 All apps are automatically converted from the upstream CasaOS App Store
 repository maintained by IceWhale Tech and packaged for HaLOS.
